headline: If I Could Buy Only 1 High-Yield Dividend Stock for Passive Income in July, This Would Be It
summary: Realty Income is the quintessential dividend stock to buy for passive income.  The REIT pays a very bankable monthly dividend.  Its strong financial profile allows it to grow its portfolio and dividend payment.
